{"tid":1222725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［614］經過今日，遮打花園正式更名為媽打花園。","createTime":"2019-06-14T13:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:55:39.000Z","uid":1863,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c1312144c629585f23ecbe79001682125315fc79","tid":1222725,"uid":1863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"今日遮打花園舉行咗一個名為「香港媽媽反送中集氣大會」嘅活動，因為原來有一班為數唔少嘅媽媽想話俾年輕人知道，我地並唔係孤單嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，呢一班平日係屋企買餸、洗衫、煮飯嘅老母的確係比較和理非一啲，但係無論如何，我亦都十分欣賞佢地，因為佢地拒絕做沉默裏等待滅亡的一群。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至連我個平時甚少理會政治嘅老媽子，居然都出咗去集會，仲話代表埋係外地讀書嘅我去埋一份，我真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望香港呢一波嘅革命結束之後，大家唔會忘記呢一班媽媽亦都曾經為香港嘅民主出過一分力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">媽打們 香港勝在有妳！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xk0HF2Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXk0HF2Z.png&h=fa6cb283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TPAwzo0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTPAwzo0.png&h=84ad7b87&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"657f87f3b39411c6a62c75b3df30cec1f70c3f73","tid":1222725,"uid":1863,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"可能各位而家心中都好灰，甚至覺得呢一場革命係輸緊，但係請記住，老母們一如以往係我地後面！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}